WEBVTT

00:00:18.720 --> 00:00:19.600 line:80%
Your Highness!

00:00:20.280 --> 00:00:21.350 line:80%
Can you swim?

00:00:23.120 --> 00:00:24.030 line:80%
Swim?

00:00:27.800 --> 00:00:28.720 line:80%
Swim?

00:00:30.080 --> 00:00:31.600 line:80%
So that's it.

00:00:31.870 --> 00:00:34.590 line:80%
Xie Zheng planned to burst the dam
from the very beginning.

00:00:34.590 --> 00:00:37.120 line:80%
That's why he only brought 1000 men
as a decoy.

00:00:41.270 --> 00:00:43.230 line:80%
Well done, Marquis of Wu'an.

00:00:43.230 --> 00:00:45.720 line:80%
What a truly profitable deal.

00:00:50.360 --> 00:00:50.730 line:80%
Hyah!

00:00:50.760 --> 00:00:51.260 line:80%
Hyah!

00:00:51.280 --> 00:00:52.300 line:80%
Hyah!

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:53.230 line:80%
Hyah!

00:00:54.120 --> 00:00:54.950 line:80%
It's a trap?

00:00:55.680 --> 00:00:57.040 line:80%
Don't come in!

00:00:57.040 --> 00:01:00.190 line:80%
All of you! Retreat!

00:01:06.030 --> 00:01:10.230 line:80%
All of you! Retreat!

00:01:12.870 --> 00:01:14.070 line:80%
Here comes the water!

00:01:16.080 --> 00:01:17.120 line:80%
Run!

00:01:29.130 --> 00:01:29.580 line:80%
[He]

00:01:41.870 --> 00:01:43.080 line:80%
The second mouse

00:01:43.080 --> 00:01:44.150 line:80%
enjoys the cheese.

00:01:44.510 --> 00:01:46.670 line:80%
They surely didn't expect you
to have a backup plan.

00:01:46.670 --> 00:01:48.589 line:80%
This plan will surely trap Xie Zheng.

00:01:48.589 --> 00:01:49.390 line:80%
From now on,

00:01:49.390 --> 00:01:52.850 line:80%
you will be the only Heir Apparent
of Lord Changxin's Mansion.

00:01:57.150 --> 00:01:58.000 line:80%
Oh no.

00:01:59.200 --> 00:02:00.280 line:80%
The manor is on low ground.

00:02:00.280 --> 00:02:01.680 line:80%
It will be flooded first.

00:02:03.310 --> 00:02:04.910 line:80%
Master, where are you going?

00:02:05.200 --> 00:02:06.390 line:80%
Don't be rash!

00:02:07.230 --> 00:02:07.880 line:80%
Hyah!

00:02:08.430 --> 00:02:09.990 line:80%
Master, wrong way!

00:02:09.990 --> 00:02:11.320 line:80%
That way is the manor!

00:02:16.270 --> 00:02:17.670 line:80%
Run!

00:02:26.480 --> 00:02:27.480 line:80%
Are you hurt?

00:02:27.760 --> 00:02:28.830 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:02:31.610 --> 00:02:33.250 line:80%
[539] [545]

00:02:40.390 --> 00:02:41.360 line:80%
What is this?

00:02:42.830 --> 00:02:43.550 line:80%
Mancang.

00:02:44.920 --> 00:02:46.990 line:80%
What do you think it's used for?

00:02:47.550 --> 00:02:48.830 line:80%
There's a string here.

00:02:49.320 --> 00:02:50.590 line:80%
Pull it and see.

00:03:00.480 --> 00:03:02.430 line:80%
Your scout is certainly dutiful.

00:03:02.950 --> 00:03:04.920 line:80%
He's still signaling you to flee.

00:03:06.200 --> 00:03:08.460 line:80%
Why don't you try to flee, Your Highness?

00:03:17.220 --> 00:03:18.810 line:80%
[Sui]

00:03:22.080 --> 00:03:24.160 line:80%
Xie Qi, take him away.

00:03:28.200 --> 00:03:29.230 line:80%
Who told you to touch that?

00:03:29.230 --> 00:03:30.510 line:80%
Didn't he ask for it?

00:03:31.910 --> 00:03:32.710 line:80%
He did it.

00:03:33.550 --> 00:03:35.750 line:80%
So you just did it because he told you to?

00:03:35.760 --> 00:03:37.490 line:80%
-No. No.
-Do you want a beating?

00:03:38.160 --> 00:03:38.690 line:80%
Brother!

00:03:38.800 --> 00:03:39.430 line:80%
Restless hands!

00:03:39.430 --> 00:03:39.960 line:80%
Brother!

00:03:40.510 --> 00:03:41.040 line:80%
Beat him!

00:03:41.830 --> 00:03:42.670 line:80%
Harder!

00:03:42.830 --> 00:03:43.830 line:80%
I understand now.

00:03:44.040 --> 00:03:45.550 line:80%
That man kowtowed and begged me for mercy,

00:03:45.550 --> 00:03:47.430 line:80%
but he was actually
trying to send a signal.

00:03:47.430 --> 00:03:49.360 line:80%
What Master wanted me to intercept

00:03:50.160 --> 00:03:50.920 line:80%
was this.

00:03:53.110 --> 00:03:55.110 line:80%
Your Lordship, this injury is too severe.

00:03:55.110 --> 00:03:56.800 line:80%
It needs immediate treatment.

00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:57.950 line:80%
I know what I'm doing.

00:03:57.950 --> 00:03:59.430 line:80%
Do not let others know about this.

00:03:59.430 --> 00:04:04.450 line:80%
[He]

00:04:00.430 --> 00:04:01.600 line:80%
You really need

00:04:01.600 --> 00:04:02.640 line:80%
to change your temper.

00:04:02.640 --> 00:04:03.880 line:80%
Get some rest. Let me do it.

00:04:03.880 --> 00:04:04.810 line:80%
Come, let me see.

00:04:06.040 --> 00:04:07.440 line:80%
You're still burning up.

00:04:09.880 --> 00:04:11.200 line:80%
Changning has been traveling for days,

00:04:11.200 --> 00:04:13.040 line:80%
and she's been badly frightened.

00:04:13.040 --> 00:04:15.040 line:80%
This illness will take time to heal.

00:04:15.670 --> 00:04:17.069 line:80%
How should we settle her?

00:04:18.040 --> 00:04:19.500 line:80%
When she gets a bit better,

00:04:19.550 --> 00:04:21.480 line:80%
send someone to take her back to Jizhou.

00:04:21.480 --> 00:04:22.990 line:80%
Her sister must be burning with anxiety

00:04:22.990 --> 00:04:24.360 line:80%
at home.

00:04:25.920 --> 00:04:26.630 line:80%
Changning,

00:04:27.280 --> 00:04:28.880 line:80%
this is your sister's candy.

00:04:29.110 --> 00:04:30.310 line:80%
Do you miss her?

00:04:32.630 --> 00:04:33.480 line:80%
Have a candy.

00:04:36.230 --> 00:04:37.800 line:80%
Will you ever learn?

00:04:37.920 --> 00:04:39.180 line:80%
Who is on the mountain?

00:04:39.720 --> 00:04:41.450 line:80%
How dare you signal the rebels?

00:04:41.870 --> 00:04:42.750 line:80%
Who are you?

00:04:44.550 --> 00:04:46.680 line:80%
I am a scout under the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:04:46.870 --> 00:04:47.959 line:80%
What you are holding

00:04:47.959 --> 00:04:51.820 line:80%
is a whistling arrow launcher
that the Sui Army uses to signal alarms.

00:04:54.750 --> 00:04:56.680 line:80%
We are laborers repairing the dam.

00:04:56.990 --> 00:04:58.920 line:80%
An enemy discovered the plan
to breach the dam

00:04:58.920 --> 00:05:00.780 line:80%
and wanted to warn the rebel army.

00:05:00.840 --> 00:05:02.700 line:80%
We chased him here and killed him.

00:05:03.400 --> 00:05:05.610 line:80%
If we hadn't dealt with those villains,

00:05:06.110 --> 00:05:08.710 line:80%
the Marquis of Wu'an's plan
would have failed.

00:05:10.230 --> 00:05:11.990 line:80%
Here are the tokens of those scouts.

00:05:11.990 --> 00:05:14.250 line:80%
See for yourself if you don't believe us.

00:05:16.720 --> 00:05:18.650 line:80%
It seems to be a misunderstanding.

00:05:18.960 --> 00:05:20.960 line:80%
You brave souls have guts.

00:05:22.520 --> 00:05:24.310 line:80%
What are your names?

00:05:24.840 --> 00:05:25.520 line:80%
My...

00:05:26.390 --> 00:05:28.510 line:80%
Be humble. No need to claim credit.

00:05:28.660 --> 00:05:29.390 line:80%
Hyah!

00:05:29.960 --> 00:05:30.600 line:80%
Hyah!

00:05:32.800 --> 00:05:33.660 line:80%
Your Lordship.

00:05:35.840 --> 00:05:37.430 line:80%
General He
ordered me to report immediately.

00:05:37.430 --> 00:05:38.480 line:80%
General Shi Yue of the rebel army

00:05:38.480 --> 00:05:40.209 line:80%
has led the army to surround us.

00:05:40.920 --> 00:05:42.450 line:80%
Your Lordship, Counselor.

00:05:42.720 --> 00:05:44.850 line:80%
Please break out with me immediately.

00:05:45.040 --> 00:05:48.040 line:80%
Shi Yue... is a fierce general
under Lord Changxin.

00:05:48.040 --> 00:05:49.370 line:80%
He is a capable fighter.

00:05:49.920 --> 00:05:51.450 line:80%
How many men did they bring?

00:05:51.750 --> 00:05:53.110 line:80%
A full 30,000.

00:05:53.110 --> 00:05:53.720 line:80%
Thirty...

00:05:57.550 --> 00:05:59.209 line:80%
We have suffered heavy losses

00:05:59.360 --> 00:06:01.090 line:80%
and have less than 800 men left.

00:06:01.230 --> 00:06:03.030 line:80%
There is no hope of breaking out.

00:06:03.870 --> 00:06:07.130 line:80%
It really is a case of "the second mouse
enjoys the cheese."

00:06:08.990 --> 00:06:09.800 line:80%
Xie Wu.

00:06:10.360 --> 00:06:11.630 line:80%
Go and settle Changning down.

00:06:11.630 --> 00:06:12.230 line:80%
Yes.

00:06:13.840 --> 00:06:14.700 line:80%
Your Lordship.

00:06:15.230 --> 00:06:16.630 line:80%
Do you plan to stay?

00:06:18.230 --> 00:06:20.110 line:80%
But you have less than 1,000 men.

00:06:20.110 --> 00:06:22.400 line:80%
How can you fight Shi Yue's army
of tens of thousands?

00:06:22.400 --> 00:06:23.990 line:80%
The main army of Yanzhou

00:06:23.990 --> 00:06:25.450 line:80%
is marching toward Baxia.

00:06:26.430 --> 00:06:29.110 line:80%
Please go back and inform Old General He

00:06:29.870 --> 00:06:32.160 line:80%
that I will meet him
around the Spring Equinox

00:06:32.160 --> 00:06:33.690 line:80%
for a hunt at North Mount Gu.

00:06:33.840 --> 00:06:34.400 line:80%
Yes.

00:06:35.110 --> 00:06:35.870 line:80%
General He,

00:06:36.310 --> 00:06:37.970 line:80%
lead the main army to retreat.

00:06:38.040 --> 00:06:39.870 line:80%
Shi Yue is after the Xie Army.

00:06:40.230 --> 00:06:43.070 line:80%
As long as my troops
and Sui Yuanqing are here,

00:06:43.480 --> 00:06:45.400 line:80%
he won't waste time chasing you.

00:06:45.630 --> 00:06:46.550 line:80%
But...

00:06:48.840 --> 00:06:50.550 line:80%
Your Lordship, Counselor.

00:06:51.160 --> 00:06:51.800 line:80%
Take care.

00:06:53.090 --> 00:06:53.850 line:80%
Take care.

00:06:55.360 --> 00:06:57.440 line:80%
Jizhou Army, retreat with me!

00:06:58.070 --> 00:07:03.040 line:80%
[Marquis of Wu'an]

00:07:03.360 --> 00:07:04.430 line:80%
Pass on my order!

00:07:04.840 --> 00:07:06.500 line:80%
The whole army is to break camp

00:07:06.630 --> 00:07:08.800 line:80%
and move to the Mount Gu Camp!

00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:09.990 line:80%
Hyah!

00:07:10.040 --> 00:07:11.160 line:80%
-Hyah!
-Yes!

00:07:10.110 --> 00:07:14.060 line:80%
[Marquis of Wu'an]

00:07:11.160 --> 00:07:11.840 line:80%
Hyah!

00:07:20.630 --> 00:07:23.840 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an's army
is indeed mighty.

00:07:24.360 --> 00:07:26.570 line:80%
And quite cool.

00:07:35.959 --> 00:07:38.020 line:80%
May Heaven bless the Marquis of Wu'an

00:07:38.520 --> 00:07:39.990 line:80%
and our soldiers

00:07:40.800 --> 00:07:42.070 line:80%
to go safely

00:07:42.790 --> 00:07:44.030 line:80%
and return safely.

00:07:58.550 --> 00:07:59.550 line:80%
Report!

00:07:59.720 --> 00:08:00.840 line:80%
The dam at Baxia has burst.

00:08:00.840 --> 00:08:02.240 line:80%
The Sui Army
suffered countless casualties.

00:08:02.240 --> 00:08:03.440 line:80%
The Heir Apparent...

00:08:03.550 --> 00:08:05.520 line:80%
was captured alive
by the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:08:05.520 --> 00:08:06.230 line:80%
Brother.

00:08:05.700 --> 00:08:08.920 line:80%
[Shi Hu]

00:08:06.430 --> 00:08:08.160 line:80%
This Xie Zheng has gone too far.

00:08:08.280 --> 00:08:09.400 line:80%
Let's make him pay with blood!

00:08:09.400 --> 00:08:10.110 line:80%
Hu!

00:08:09.600 --> 00:08:13.420 line:80%
[Shi Yue]

00:08:11.360 --> 00:08:13.360 line:80%
We must stay calm at a time like this.

00:08:15.670 --> 00:08:17.480 line:80%
-Fortunately, the Eldest Young Master planned it perfectly
-Yes.

00:08:17.480 --> 00:08:18.840 line:80%
and had us rush here

00:08:19.160 --> 00:08:22.190 line:80%
so that we could intercept
the Marquis of Wu'an's troops.

00:08:22.190 --> 00:08:24.720 line:80%
Let's go meet this Marquis of Wu'an.

00:08:26.040 --> 00:08:28.840 line:80%
We'll find a way
to rescue the Heir Apparent first.

00:08:43.430 --> 00:08:44.950 line:80%
Master!

00:08:45.430 --> 00:08:46.310 line:80%
Old man!

00:08:46.670 --> 00:08:47.640 line:80%
We're back!

00:08:51.160 --> 00:08:52.600 line:80%
Master!

00:09:00.020 --> 00:09:05.190 line:80%
[545]

00:09:01.000 --> 00:09:01.880 line:80%
We did it.

00:09:02.920 --> 00:09:04.320 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an won!

00:09:05.800 --> 00:09:06.800 line:80%
We won!

00:09:06.950 --> 00:09:07.900 line:80%
We won!

00:09:08.710 --> 00:09:09.580 line:80%
We won!

00:09:09.670 --> 00:09:10.720 line:80%
We won!

00:09:11.590 --> 00:09:12.430 line:80%
We did it.

00:09:12.450 --> 00:09:13.450 line:80%
We won!

00:09:15.150 --> 00:09:16.500 line:80%
[545]

00:09:16.670 --> 00:09:17.800 line:80%
Good!

00:09:20.880 --> 00:09:23.190 line:80%
Who says women are inferior to men?

00:09:24.650 --> 00:09:25.650 line:80%
I certainly chose

00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:30.110 line:80%
a good disciple.

00:10:56.770 --> 00:11:02.230 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:11:02.310 --> 00:11:04.920 line:80%
[Episode 23]

00:12:18.550 --> 00:12:19.690 line:80%
Yu Qianqian.

00:12:20.520 --> 00:12:21.190 line:80%
Wake up!

00:12:22.070 --> 00:12:22.920 line:80%
Yu Qianqian!

00:12:23.440 --> 00:12:24.860 line:80%
I won't let you die!

00:12:41.800 --> 00:12:42.760 line:80%
Qianqian.

00:13:18.590 --> 00:13:19.650 line:80%
Where are we going?

00:13:21.070 --> 00:13:22.350 line:80%
Does it matter?

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:25.550 line:80%
You go where I go.

00:13:26.480 --> 00:13:28.480 line:80%
You can't leave my side for a second.

00:13:55.240 --> 00:13:57.730 line:80%
Stop! I can't hold it anymore.

00:14:02.070 --> 00:14:03.140 line:80%
-Little Young Master!
-Uncle Xun!

00:14:03.140 --> 00:14:04.590 line:80%
-Be careful.
-My stomach hurts!

00:14:04.590 --> 00:14:05.830 line:80%
Watch your step.

00:14:14.280 --> 00:14:15.310 line:80%
Be careful.

00:14:15.830 --> 00:14:16.670 line:80%
Mrs. Lan,

00:14:16.950 --> 00:14:18.640 line:80%
we're almost at the Jizhou border.

00:14:18.640 --> 00:14:21.520 line:80%
Will the Marquis of Wu'an
really join forces with us?

00:14:21.520 --> 00:14:23.800 line:80%
With Shi Yue's army of 30,000 before him,

00:14:24.040 --> 00:14:26.370 line:80%
he might be hard-pressed to save himself.

00:14:27.120 --> 00:14:29.350 line:80%
Shi Yue may be brave and cunning,

00:14:29.430 --> 00:14:31.310 line:80%
but his opponent is the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:14:31.310 --> 00:14:32.950 line:80%
so nothing is certain yet.

00:14:33.430 --> 00:14:34.350 line:80%
Master's...

00:14:36.280 --> 00:14:39.040 line:80%
All the schemes devised
by Qi Min and Sui Yuanqing

00:14:39.040 --> 00:14:41.970 line:80%
were broken by the Marquis of Wu'an
against all odds.

00:14:42.190 --> 00:14:43.120 line:80%
I believe

00:14:43.550 --> 00:14:45.590 line:80%
he will win this time too.

00:14:46.800 --> 00:14:47.530 line:80%
Who's there?

00:15:31.430 --> 00:15:33.040 line:80%
Nanny, do you really think

00:15:33.520 --> 00:15:35.160 line:80%
you can escape safely

00:15:35.550 --> 00:15:37.470 line:80%
with that brat

00:15:38.800 --> 00:15:40.950 line:80%
and defect to the Marquis of Wu'an?

00:15:42.800 --> 00:15:45.280 line:80%
It seems you have forgotten

00:15:46.000 --> 00:15:48.060 line:80%
all my mother's instructions to you.

00:15:49.070 --> 00:15:50.800 line:80%
Precisely because I haven't forgotten,

00:15:50.800 --> 00:15:53.280 line:80%
I must make the right choice.

00:15:53.860 --> 00:15:56.340 line:80%
Her highness was truly pitiable back then.

00:15:56.560 --> 00:15:57.880 line:80%
She actually gave her own life

00:15:57.880 --> 00:16:00.160 line:80%
to save a madman like you.

00:16:00.830 --> 00:16:03.160 line:80%
Have you forgotten
the Crown Prince Chengde's hatred,

00:16:03.160 --> 00:16:04.640 line:80%
or how your mother died tragically

00:16:04.640 --> 00:16:06.760 line:80%
right in front of you?

00:16:11.520 --> 00:16:12.850 line:80%
That feels much better.

00:16:14.100 --> 00:16:14.840 line:80%
Bao'er.

00:16:17.120 --> 00:16:18.430 line:80%
I remember

00:16:19.280 --> 00:16:23.850 line:80%
how Father was disemboweled
by the Beijue people.

00:16:24.470 --> 00:16:25.920 line:80%
I also remember

00:16:26.470 --> 00:16:29.510 line:80%
the pain of my flesh splitting open
from the fire.

00:16:30.470 --> 00:16:31.950 line:80%
It hurt so much

00:16:32.470 --> 00:16:34.520 line:80%
that I no longer feel any pain now.

00:16:35.550 --> 00:16:36.930 line:80%
I also remember

00:16:38.040 --> 00:16:41.260 line:80%
Mother's wails as she was burned alive.

00:16:48.070 --> 00:16:49.240 line:80%
Live on.

00:16:55.920 --> 00:16:56.830 line:80%
And you,

00:16:58.270 --> 00:16:59.840 line:80%
you speak of even betrayal

00:17:00.510 --> 00:17:03.050 line:80%
with such high-sounding righteousness.

00:17:14.760 --> 00:17:18.590 line:80%
Where there is life, there is hope!

00:17:18.850 --> 00:17:21.580 line:80%
Where there is life, there is hope!

00:17:22.629 --> 00:17:25.800 line:80%
Where there is life, there is hope!

00:17:44.590 --> 00:17:45.550 line:80%
What?

00:17:47.080 --> 00:17:49.100 line:80%
Have you finally decided

00:17:50.200 --> 00:17:52.280 line:80%
to kill the child

00:17:53.350 --> 00:17:54.960 line:80%
you raised yourself?

00:17:56.680 --> 00:17:58.760 line:80%
But I don't want to die yet.

00:18:04.630 --> 00:18:05.890 line:80%
What should I do?

00:18:16.480 --> 00:18:19.280 line:80%
An emperor must not be blinded by love.

00:18:19.440 --> 00:18:21.590 line:80%
You can fool the world,

00:18:21.760 --> 00:18:24.880 line:80%
but you're being played for a fool
by a woman.

00:18:25.150 --> 00:18:27.390 line:80%
You love Yu Qianqian so much.

00:18:29.440 --> 00:18:31.000 line:80%
But you know what?

00:18:31.550 --> 00:18:33.540 line:80%
She said many times

00:18:33.870 --> 00:18:35.310 line:80%
that Bao'er could only survive

00:18:35.310 --> 00:18:37.350 line:80%
if you died.

00:18:52.390 --> 00:18:55.690 line:80%
I wanted to take her with me,

00:18:56.000 --> 00:18:57.550 line:80%
but she said

00:18:57.550 --> 00:19:00.440 line:80%
we couldn't escape unless you died.

00:19:01.590 --> 00:19:03.230 line:80%
She said...

00:19:03.800 --> 00:19:08.310 line:80%
she would kill you herself.

00:19:27.930 --> 00:19:29.080 line:80%
I wanted to kill you.

00:19:30.680 --> 00:19:32.310 line:80%
Why did you save me?

00:19:33.040 --> 00:19:34.630 line:80%
Your life belongs to me.

00:19:35.070 --> 00:19:36.670 line:80%
Without my permission,

00:19:37.240 --> 00:19:39.390 line:80%
no one can let you die.

00:19:45.760 --> 00:19:47.630 line:80%
Little Young Master, let's go.

00:20:03.310 --> 00:20:04.830 line:80%
When you see my mother,

00:20:05.830 --> 00:20:07.070 line:80%
pay my respects.

00:20:21.350 --> 00:20:22.480 line:80%
Give her a proper burial.

00:20:22.480 --> 00:20:23.270 line:80%
Yes.

00:20:23.480 --> 00:20:25.340 line:80%
What about Zhao Xun and Little...

00:20:25.580 --> 00:20:27.640 line:80%
"Where there is life, there is hope."

00:20:28.550 --> 00:20:30.950 line:80%
That doesn't sound like
it was meant for me.

00:20:31.280 --> 00:20:32.630 line:80%
They must be nearby.

00:20:33.310 --> 00:20:34.310 line:80%
I want them alive.

00:20:34.670 --> 00:20:35.230 line:80%
Yes.

00:20:35.740 --> 00:20:36.330 line:80%
Search!

00:20:58.750 --> 00:21:00.610 line:80%
You wanted to sacrifice yourself

00:21:00.630 --> 00:21:01.800 line:80%
to kill me,

00:21:02.310 --> 00:21:04.550 line:80%
just to protect that brat.

00:21:05.630 --> 00:21:08.430 line:80%
Why couldn't you bring yourself
to do it in the end?

00:21:09.520 --> 00:21:11.320 line:80%
I couldn't bring myself to do it?

00:21:11.520 --> 00:21:12.630 line:80%
I failed once,

00:21:13.030 --> 00:21:14.890 line:80%
but there's always a second time.

00:21:14.960 --> 00:21:16.220 line:80%
If I fail a second time,

00:21:16.520 --> 00:21:17.760 line:80%
there's a third.

00:21:17.960 --> 00:21:19.590 line:80%
One day, I will kill you.

00:21:22.480 --> 00:21:23.800 line:80%
If you kill me,

00:21:24.400 --> 00:21:26.730 line:80%
someone else will kill that brat.

00:21:27.480 --> 00:21:30.080 line:80%
If they fail once,
they'll try the second time.

00:21:30.590 --> 00:21:32.190 line:80%
If they fail the second time,

00:21:33.630 --> 00:21:35.110 line:80%
there's a third time.

00:21:36.720 --> 00:21:38.580 line:80%
If you dare do anything to Bao'er,

00:21:38.720 --> 00:21:39.910 line:80%
I won't live either!

00:21:41.680 --> 00:21:42.870 line:80%
So,

00:21:45.870 --> 00:21:47.330 line:80%
our family of three

00:21:47.440 --> 00:21:49.040 line:80%
must all live well.

00:21:54.680 --> 00:21:58.410 line:80%
[North Mount Gu Camp]

00:21:56.590 --> 00:21:57.310 line:80%
Hyah!

00:21:57.720 --> 00:21:58.310 line:80%
Hyah!

00:21:59.310 --> 00:21:59.910 line:80%
Hyah!

00:22:07.140 --> 00:22:08.110 line:80%
You're badly hurt.

00:22:08.110 --> 00:22:08.830 line:80%
You shouldn't be out here.

00:22:08.830 --> 00:22:09.550 line:80%
Go back and rest.

00:22:09.550 --> 00:22:10.280 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:22:11.480 --> 00:22:12.740 line:80%
If I don't show my face,

00:22:12.960 --> 00:22:14.910 line:80%
who will steady the troops' morale?

00:22:14.910 --> 00:22:15.590 line:80%
Slow down.

00:22:17.390 --> 00:22:19.720 line:80%
Although the Mount Gu Camp is old,

00:22:19.720 --> 00:22:21.000 line:80%
the terrain is excellent.

00:22:21.000 --> 00:22:22.800 line:80%
It's easy to defend and hard to attack.

00:22:22.800 --> 00:22:25.350 line:80%
And with the hundreds of soldiers
stationed here,

00:22:25.350 --> 00:22:27.310 line:80%
Shi Yue and Shi Hu won't break in easily.

00:22:27.310 --> 00:22:27.970 line:80%
Let go of me!

00:22:28.680 --> 00:22:30.240 line:80%
With this broken camp,

00:22:31.480 --> 00:22:33.340 line:80%
you really think you can hold out?

00:22:34.350 --> 00:22:35.680 line:80%
You're cooked.

00:22:36.590 --> 00:22:37.440 line:80%
Your Lordship,

00:22:37.440 --> 00:22:38.900 line:80%
what should we do with him?

00:22:38.910 --> 00:22:40.110 line:80%
Lock him in the dungeon
in the back mountain.

00:22:40.110 --> 00:22:40.720 line:80%
Yes.

00:22:41.200 --> 00:22:42.000 line:80%
Take him away.

00:22:42.240 --> 00:22:43.630 line:80%
You're cooked!

00:22:45.090 --> 00:22:46.610 line:80%
You're cooked!

00:22:49.590 --> 00:22:50.450 line:80%
Your Lordship.

00:22:50.680 --> 00:22:52.800 line:80%
Yesterday, a few laborers
repairing the dam on the mountain

00:22:52.800 --> 00:22:54.150 line:80%
spotted the enemy scouts

00:22:54.150 --> 00:22:55.310 line:80%
and killed all three of them,

00:22:55.310 --> 00:22:57.440 line:80%
preventing them from warning the others.

00:22:57.440 --> 00:22:59.500 line:80%
That's why Sui Yuanqing got tricked.

00:22:59.520 --> 00:23:01.310 line:80%
Do you remember their names?

00:23:01.540 --> 00:23:02.690 line:80%
They earned their merit.

00:23:02.690 --> 00:23:04.240 line:80%
Jizhou should reward them.

00:23:05.040 --> 00:23:06.720 line:80%
Counselor, we do.

00:23:07.030 --> 00:23:08.910 line:80%
They call themselves
the Northwest Pig Butcher Squad.

00:23:08.910 --> 00:23:10.240 line:80%
Hard to forget, really.

00:23:10.350 --> 00:23:12.110 line:80%
What are your names?

00:23:12.320 --> 00:23:13.010 line:80%
I...

00:23:13.150 --> 00:23:15.110 line:80%
Be humble. No need to claim credit.

00:23:15.830 --> 00:23:16.960 line:80%
Tell them who we are.

00:23:20.280 --> 00:23:21.680 line:80%
We are...

00:23:22.440 --> 00:23:26.280 line:80%
the Northwest Pig Butcher Squad!

00:23:32.770 --> 00:23:34.730 line:80%
The Northwest Pig Butcher Squad?

00:23:34.760 --> 00:23:35.610 line:80%
You may leave.

00:23:35.870 --> 00:23:36.430 line:80%
Yes.

00:23:40.390 --> 00:23:42.310 line:80%
The Northwest Pig Butcher Squad.

00:23:43.110 --> 00:23:44.720 line:80%
This name is quite unique.

00:23:47.310 --> 00:23:48.840 line:80%
That reminds me of someone.

00:23:52.820 --> 00:23:53.890 line:80%
Impossible.

00:23:54.550 --> 00:23:57.610 line:80%
She's in Jizhou with Li Huai'an
looking for Changning.

00:23:58.970 --> 00:24:00.170 line:80%
But you did remind me.

00:24:00.830 --> 00:24:02.430 line:80%
Since Changning is safe now,

00:24:03.000 --> 00:24:04.390 line:80%
I should let her know,

00:24:04.800 --> 00:24:05.860 line:80%
so she won't worry.

00:24:18.150 --> 00:24:19.550 line:80%
This is a temporary shed.

00:24:21.800 --> 00:24:22.590 line:80%
Mrs. Fan,

00:24:22.800 --> 00:24:25.110 line:80%
most of the sheds earlier were destroyed.

00:24:25.110 --> 00:24:27.510 line:80%
Please rest
in this temporary shed for now.

00:24:27.960 --> 00:24:28.720 line:80%
Thank you.

00:24:29.440 --> 00:24:30.700 line:80%
Where are my brothers?

00:24:31.720 --> 00:24:33.580 line:80%
Grand Tutor Tao took them to rest.

00:24:33.830 --> 00:24:35.560 line:80%
The buns the kitchen made today

00:24:35.630 --> 00:24:37.420 line:80%
are as hard as the iron we forge.

00:24:37.550 --> 00:24:38.640 line:80%
I just took a bite,

00:24:38.800 --> 00:24:40.520 line:80%
and it almost broke my teeth.

00:24:40.960 --> 00:24:41.720 line:80%
Sir,

00:24:41.830 --> 00:24:43.560 line:80%
do you think this spear is okay?

00:24:44.030 --> 00:24:47.050 line:80%
[Smith]

00:24:44.110 --> 00:24:46.000 line:80%
The quenching heat for spearheads

00:24:46.000 --> 00:24:47.310 line:80%
must be controlled precisely.

00:24:47.310 --> 00:24:48.420 line:80%
If it's too brittle,

00:24:48.420 --> 00:24:49.700 line:80%
it will break easily.

00:24:50.370 --> 00:24:51.600 line:80%
Be careful next time.

00:24:52.660 --> 00:24:54.180 line:80%
M-Mr. Zhao?

00:24:54.110 --> 00:24:55.910 line:80%
[Smith]

00:25:01.070 --> 00:25:03.440 line:80%
-Changyu?
-Who is this young lady?

00:25:04.890 --> 00:25:06.520 line:80%
[Smith]

00:25:07.440 --> 00:25:08.680 line:80%
M-Mr. Zhao!

00:25:08.840 --> 00:25:10.750 line:80%
[Smith]

00:25:10.110 --> 00:25:10.960 line:80%
Changyu!

00:25:12.150 --> 00:25:13.040 line:80%
Mr. Zhao!

00:25:13.910 --> 00:25:16.570 line:80%
Changyu, why have you come
to the military camp?

00:25:17.520 --> 00:25:18.200 line:80%
I...

00:25:20.100 --> 00:25:21.560 line:80%
Mrs. Chen,

00:25:22.150 --> 00:25:23.480 line:80%
Mrs. Zhuang,

00:25:24.480 --> 00:25:25.700 line:80%
Auntie Tao,

00:25:26.590 --> 00:25:27.960 line:80%
and Xiaohu

00:25:30.480 --> 00:25:31.780 line:80%
are all alive.

00:25:36.720 --> 00:25:39.240 line:80%
Poor Wang and Granny Kang.

00:25:39.770 --> 00:25:41.460 line:80%
They just died like that.

00:25:47.280 --> 00:25:49.410 line:80%
I haven't found Changning yet either.

00:25:52.750 --> 00:25:54.430 line:80%
Changning

00:25:54.630 --> 00:25:56.040 line:80%
has a round lucky face.

00:25:56.240 --> 00:25:57.590 line:80%
She will surely be fine.

00:26:00.440 --> 00:26:01.970 line:80%
I will definitely find her,

00:26:02.350 --> 00:26:03.880 line:80%
no matter how long it takes.

00:26:05.000 --> 00:26:07.000 line:80%
And you. Take care of yourself.

00:26:07.240 --> 00:26:09.240 line:80%
Mrs. Zhao is waiting for you at home.

00:26:10.440 --> 00:26:11.480 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:26:11.870 --> 00:26:13.440 line:80%
I can treat livestock,

00:26:13.440 --> 00:26:16.240 line:80%
and I learned some blacksmithing
when I was young.

00:26:16.240 --> 00:26:17.440 line:80%
In this camp,

00:26:17.440 --> 00:26:19.590 line:80%
shoeing and treating illnesses

00:26:19.650 --> 00:26:20.730 line:80%
for the livestock

00:26:20.760 --> 00:26:22.390 line:80%
and repairing weapons—

00:26:22.410 --> 00:26:24.930 line:80%
they rely on me for all of that.

00:26:25.870 --> 00:26:28.350 line:80%
But Mr. Jin and those brats

00:26:28.370 --> 00:26:30.070 line:80%
have really impressed me.

00:26:30.350 --> 00:26:31.480 line:80%
Can you believe they

00:26:31.520 --> 00:26:33.500 line:80%
stopped their petty thievery

00:26:33.520 --> 00:26:34.480 line:80%
and joined the army?

00:26:34.480 --> 00:26:35.880 line:80%
It's a good thing, right?

00:26:41.630 --> 00:26:43.630 line:80%
You've been here for so long.

00:26:44.150 --> 00:26:45.830 line:80%
Is there any news of Yan Zheng?

00:26:46.720 --> 00:26:48.280 line:80%
Was that bundle delivered?

00:26:51.200 --> 00:26:53.670 line:80%
I asked someone to deliver the things,

00:26:54.040 --> 00:26:55.390 line:80%
but he didn't see him.

00:26:56.830 --> 00:26:58.040 line:80%
I asked about him.

00:26:58.150 --> 00:27:00.200 line:80%
He's not in this supply unit.

00:27:03.240 --> 00:27:04.520 line:80%
In the army,

00:27:04.520 --> 00:27:06.040 line:80%
there's an old saying—

00:27:07.110 --> 00:27:08.350 line:80%
"No news of death

00:27:08.350 --> 00:27:09.630 line:80%
is good news."

00:27:10.310 --> 00:27:13.110 line:80%
Don't worry.
Yan Zheng will surely be fine.

00:27:13.760 --> 00:27:15.830 line:80%
If he makes it big in the future,

00:27:15.830 --> 00:27:18.280 line:80%
you can enjoy a good life with him.

00:27:20.070 --> 00:27:21.110 line:80%
Actually,

00:27:21.520 --> 00:27:23.120 line:80%
I have already divorced him.

00:27:29.200 --> 00:27:30.480 line:80%
What happened?

00:27:31.520 --> 00:27:33.520 line:80%
It was a fake marriage to begin with.

00:27:33.590 --> 00:27:35.310 line:80%
It was just to deal with Fan Daniu
back then

00:27:35.310 --> 00:27:36.480 line:80%
and save the house.

00:27:37.150 --> 00:27:38.480 line:80%
Now that it's over,

00:27:38.800 --> 00:27:40.200 line:80%
he left.

00:27:40.200 --> 00:27:40.760 line:80%
Well...

00:27:41.310 --> 00:27:42.480 line:80%
Changyu.

00:27:42.960 --> 00:27:44.760 line:80%
Yan Zheng looked like

00:27:44.760 --> 00:27:47.350 line:80%
he had feelings for you.

00:27:49.870 --> 00:27:51.790 line:80%
Young couples inevitably

00:27:51.820 --> 00:27:55.120 line:80%
act on impulse and go astray.

00:27:55.720 --> 00:27:57.310 line:80%
If you happen to meet him in the future,

00:27:57.310 --> 00:27:59.240 line:80%
you must talk things out

00:27:59.240 --> 00:28:00.200 line:80%
with him.

00:28:00.550 --> 00:28:02.310 line:80%
Don't wait until you're old

00:28:02.310 --> 00:28:03.970 line:80%
and leave things unresolved.

00:28:10.280 --> 00:28:11.590 line:80%
If he is still alive,

00:28:12.040 --> 00:28:14.440 line:80%
I will definitely talk things out
with him.

00:28:15.070 --> 00:28:17.000 line:80%
I really know how to read faces.

00:28:17.350 --> 00:28:19.480 line:80%
Yan Zheng has a lucky long face.

00:28:19.590 --> 00:28:21.120 line:80%
He will definitely be fine.

00:28:25.070 --> 00:28:26.000 line:80%
Grand Tutor Tao.

00:28:28.040 --> 00:28:29.440 line:80%
Changyu.

00:28:30.150 --> 00:28:31.520 line:80%
Changyu!

00:28:39.960 --> 00:28:43.150 line:80%
First, let the furnace heat up quickly,

00:28:43.350 --> 00:28:45.150 line:80%
then start pulling the bellows.

00:28:45.600 --> 00:28:46.720 line:80%
When pulling the bellows,

00:28:46.720 --> 00:28:49.040 line:80%
you must follow the rhythm of the forging.

00:28:49.040 --> 00:28:51.200 line:80%
Once it turns red, we can start forging.

00:28:51.200 --> 00:28:53.800 line:80%
You must focus on the rhythm when forging.

00:28:53.800 --> 00:28:54.630 line:80%
Look.

00:28:55.870 --> 00:28:58.760 line:80%
This girl isn't studying properly with me,

00:28:58.870 --> 00:29:01.470 line:80%
but came here
to learn blacksmithing instead.

00:29:02.330 --> 00:29:03.760 line:80%
Okay. Right?

00:29:04.200 --> 00:29:05.000 line:80%
Mr. Zhao.

00:29:05.480 --> 00:29:07.110 line:80%
We are here to pick up the new weapons.

00:29:07.110 --> 00:29:08.440 line:80%
Okay, they're all here.

00:29:09.440 --> 00:29:11.240 line:80%
They're heavy. Be careful.

00:29:11.800 --> 00:29:12.720 line:80%
Let me help.

00:29:12.960 --> 00:29:14.200 line:80%
Be careful, Changyu.

00:29:14.280 --> 00:29:15.140 line:80%
They're heavy.

00:29:15.590 --> 00:29:16.480 line:80%
One more bundle.

00:29:16.480 --> 00:29:17.390 line:80%
One more bundle?

00:29:17.390 --> 00:29:18.680 line:80%
-Can you hold up?
-Yes.

00:29:18.680 --> 00:29:19.350 line:80%
Okay.

00:29:21.150 --> 00:29:21.590 line:80%
Alright.

00:29:21.590 --> 00:29:21.830 line:80%
Here.

00:29:21.830 --> 00:29:23.560 line:80%
Here's another bundle for you.

00:29:25.040 --> 00:29:25.910 line:80%
Changyu,

00:29:25.910 --> 00:29:27.480 line:80%
you're just as strong

00:29:27.480 --> 00:29:29.490 line:80%
as Fan Erniu.

00:29:29.910 --> 00:29:31.240 line:80%
I'm nowhere near as strong as my father.

00:29:31.240 --> 00:29:33.640 line:80%
He could lift my mother and me
with one hand.

00:29:33.870 --> 00:29:34.630 line:80%
Bravo!

00:29:35.480 --> 00:29:36.150 line:80%
Really nice.

00:29:36.150 --> 00:29:36.590 line:80%
Yeah.

00:29:36.590 --> 00:29:37.480 line:80%
Good.

00:29:41.480 --> 00:29:42.520 line:80%
Watch out!

00:29:44.150 --> 00:29:47.550 line:80%
-Mr. Zhao! Are you okay?
-Changyu! What are you doing?

00:29:51.630 --> 00:29:52.440 line:80%
Mr. Zhao!

00:29:54.910 --> 00:29:55.590 line:80%
Hurry.

00:29:55.720 --> 00:29:56.200 line:80%
Come on.

00:29:58.520 --> 00:29:59.780 line:80%
Are you okay, Mr. Zhao?

00:30:00.350 --> 00:30:01.520 line:80%
What could be wrong with him?

00:30:01.520 --> 00:30:03.150 line:80%
His foot got crushed!

00:30:03.800 --> 00:30:04.310 line:80%
Here.

00:30:04.590 --> 00:30:05.550 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:30:07.150 --> 00:30:09.040 line:80%
Why did you help him first

00:30:09.040 --> 00:30:10.310 line:80%
instead of me?

00:30:10.310 --> 00:30:11.440 line:80%
Who is he?

00:30:11.440 --> 00:30:12.370 line:80%
Master, come on.

00:30:12.590 --> 00:30:13.240 line:80%
Careful.

00:30:15.040 --> 00:30:15.910 line:80%
Be careful.

00:30:16.960 --> 00:30:18.280 line:80%
Careful. Careful.

00:30:18.520 --> 00:30:19.150 line:80%
Careful.

00:30:20.720 --> 00:30:21.150 line:80%
Here.

00:30:23.910 --> 00:30:25.590 line:80%
Why did you let him sit on the chair

00:30:25.590 --> 00:30:27.590 line:80%
and make me sit on this wooden stump?

00:30:29.310 --> 00:30:30.350 line:80%
You sit here then.

00:30:30.800 --> 00:30:32.130 line:80%
Let's go sit over there.

00:30:40.480 --> 00:30:41.280 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:30:42.960 --> 00:30:45.150 line:80%
I guess I stood by
the blacksmith's furnace

00:30:45.150 --> 00:30:46.550 line:80%
for too long

00:30:46.550 --> 00:30:47.760 line:80%
and the heat got to my heart.

00:30:47.760 --> 00:30:48.800 line:80%
I'm burning up inside.

00:30:48.800 --> 00:30:50.150 line:80%
I feel terrible all over.

00:30:50.150 --> 00:30:51.950 line:80%
I'll brew some medicine for you.

00:30:58.350 --> 00:30:59.520 line:80%
What's wrong with you now?

00:30:59.520 --> 00:31:01.680 line:80%
I have a headache.

00:31:01.680 --> 00:31:02.760 line:80%
A headache?

00:31:03.480 --> 00:31:05.760 line:80%
The spear shaft didn't hit your head.

00:31:07.310 --> 00:31:09.350 line:80%
You must have caught a cold
from the commotion that night.

00:31:09.350 --> 00:31:10.550 line:80%
Let's go to the medic.

00:31:10.960 --> 00:31:12.040 line:80%
I'm not going anywhere.

00:31:12.040 --> 00:31:13.440 line:80%
I'll just rest here.

00:31:15.200 --> 00:31:16.030 line:80%
Fine.

00:31:16.520 --> 00:31:18.390 line:80%
Both of you just rest here.

00:31:18.590 --> 00:31:20.650 line:80%
I'll go brew medicine for both of you.

00:31:21.390 --> 00:31:22.200 line:80%
Changyu.

00:31:22.200 --> 00:31:23.830 line:80%
My medicine must be brewed first,

00:31:23.830 --> 00:31:25.520 line:80%
or I won't drink it.

00:31:28.150 --> 00:31:29.680 line:80%
Why are you acting like a child,

00:31:29.680 --> 00:31:32.420 line:80%
fighting over who goes first
in something like this?

00:31:32.420 --> 00:31:35.070 line:80%
Don't worry.
I'll brew both at the same time.

00:31:35.070 --> 00:31:35.960 line:80%
So there's no first or last.

00:31:35.960 --> 00:31:37.720 line:80%
Then I want to drink mine first.

00:31:37.720 --> 00:31:38.630 line:80%
Fine.

00:31:59.350 --> 00:32:01.000 line:80%
Changyu told me

00:32:01.440 --> 00:32:02.910 line:80%
that to save her life,

00:32:03.200 --> 00:32:05.730 line:80%
you swapped
the life-and-death lot with her.

00:32:08.800 --> 00:32:10.660 line:80%
That was incredibly noble of you.

00:32:12.960 --> 00:32:14.110 line:80%
For that alone,

00:32:14.300 --> 00:32:16.710 line:80%
I must let you have your medicine first.

00:32:17.200 --> 00:32:19.240 line:80%
You're too kind.

00:32:19.350 --> 00:32:21.680 line:80%
I even want to kowtow to you
on her behalf.

00:32:21.680 --> 00:32:22.550 line:80%
Please don't. I can't accept that.

00:32:22.550 --> 00:32:24.480 line:80%
Please get up.

00:32:28.720 --> 00:32:31.870 line:80%
You know Mrs. Fan well?

00:32:31.870 --> 00:32:32.870 line:80%
Of course.

00:32:33.520 --> 00:32:35.960 line:80%
We've been neighbors for nearly 20 years.

00:32:36.350 --> 00:32:37.880 line:80%
She's like a daughter to me.

00:32:38.520 --> 00:32:39.910 line:80%
To be honest,

00:32:40.480 --> 00:32:43.040 line:80%
I've never met a better girl than her.

00:32:43.200 --> 00:32:44.630 line:80%
Indeed.

00:32:44.630 --> 00:32:47.520 line:80%
I've never met such a nice lady either.

00:32:51.480 --> 00:32:52.960 line:80%
Have some hot water.

00:32:53.150 --> 00:32:54.550 line:80%
It'll warm your stomach.

00:32:54.550 --> 00:32:55.800 line:80%
Thank you.

00:32:56.520 --> 00:32:58.680 line:80%
Let's toast with tea instead of wine.

00:33:00.760 --> 00:33:01.630 line:80%
Please.

00:33:01.760 --> 00:33:02.350 line:80%
Please.

00:33:02.350 --> 00:33:03.110 line:80%
Please.

00:33:21.520 --> 00:33:23.180 line:80%
Where did this army come from?

00:33:23.440 --> 00:33:24.110 line:80%
That one?

00:33:24.760 --> 00:33:26.550 line:80%
That's the supply convoy from Jizhou.

00:33:26.550 --> 00:33:28.150 line:80%
They're here to resupply the camps

00:33:28.150 --> 00:33:29.150 line:80%
near the Wu River.

00:33:33.240 --> 00:33:35.440 line:80%
One herb is missing. Xiaku grass.

00:33:37.280 --> 00:33:38.240 line:80%
It's probably in the kitchen.

00:33:38.240 --> 00:33:39.280 line:80%
It might be there.

00:33:39.800 --> 00:33:40.390 line:80%
Thanks.

00:33:46.870 --> 00:33:48.070 line:80%
Greetings, Captain.

00:33:48.280 --> 00:33:49.200 line:80%
Who's inside?

00:33:49.520 --> 00:33:50.680 line:80%
Some wounded soldiers.

00:33:50.680 --> 00:33:51.760 line:80%
And Mr. Zhao.

00:33:52.110 --> 00:33:53.000 line:80%
Mr. Zhao?

00:33:56.830 --> 00:33:58.390 line:80%
Mr. Zhao, how is your...

00:34:01.870 --> 00:34:03.280 line:80%
Li Wenkan?

00:34:03.550 --> 00:34:05.150 line:80%
What did you call me?

00:34:06.680 --> 00:34:09.939 line:80%
I'm 3 years older than your grandfather.

00:34:11.640 --> 00:34:12.570 line:80%
Grand Tutor Tao,

00:34:12.870 --> 00:34:14.200 line:80%
what are you doing here?

00:34:16.870 --> 00:34:18.390 line:80%
Look at my memory.

00:34:18.390 --> 00:34:20.950 line:80%
I forgot to tell Changyu
you'd be here today.

00:34:21.160 --> 00:34:22.080 line:80%
Changyu?

00:34:22.910 --> 00:34:23.990 line:80%
Who's here?

00:34:30.160 --> 00:34:32.550 line:80%
-What are you doing here?
-What are you doing here?

00:34:32.550 --> 00:34:34.030 line:80%
So, the heroine who hunted down the scouts

00:34:34.030 --> 00:34:36.030 line:80%
everyone in the army praises is you.

00:34:36.560 --> 00:34:37.390 line:80%
Are you hurt?

00:34:37.800 --> 00:34:39.999 line:80%
No. Thank you for your concern, My Lord.

00:34:40.870 --> 00:34:42.600 line:80%
After all this time,
you still call me My Lord.

00:34:42.600 --> 00:34:44.400 line:80%
It's a bit too distant, isn't it?

00:34:45.039 --> 00:34:46.200 line:80%
My courtesy name is Wenkan.

00:34:46.200 --> 00:34:47.430 line:80%
You can call me that.

00:34:51.030 --> 00:34:52.560 line:80%
It's from "ten years of hard study,

00:34:52.560 --> 00:34:55.289 line:80%
only to just cross the threshold
of literature."

00:34:59.120 --> 00:35:00.510 line:80%
My Lord, you are of noble status.

00:35:00.510 --> 00:35:02.280 line:80%
How could I dare call you that?

00:35:02.560 --> 00:35:03.560 line:80%
But I'll remember it.

00:35:03.560 --> 00:35:05.220 line:80%
"Li Threshold." Sounds nice.

00:35:09.430 --> 00:35:11.090 line:80%
Thank you for the compliment.

00:35:11.740 --> 00:35:13.950 line:80%
That kid doesn't look like a good egg.

00:35:14.680 --> 00:35:16.120 line:80%
What egg? Is it tasty?

00:35:17.310 --> 00:35:18.310 line:80%
I mean that Li.

00:35:18.310 --> 00:35:19.370 line:80%
He's not a good egg.

00:35:20.350 --> 00:35:22.350 line:80%
Are you heading to Lucheng, My Lord?

00:35:23.390 --> 00:35:24.310 line:80%
Lucheng's supplies

00:35:24.310 --> 00:35:25.990 line:80%
must be delivered within 7 days.

00:35:25.990 --> 00:35:27.600 line:80%
Although I don't know what General He
and the Marquis of Wu'an

00:35:27.600 --> 00:35:28.400 line:80%
are plotting,

00:35:28.760 --> 00:35:29.870 line:80%
as the escort officer,

00:35:29.870 --> 00:35:30.640 line:80%
I must fulfill my mission.

00:35:30.640 --> 00:35:32.440 line:80%
I will ensure it arrives on time.

00:35:33.430 --> 00:35:35.830 line:80%
How about I send someone to take you back
to Jizhou?

00:35:35.830 --> 00:35:37.600 line:80%
Maybe there's news about Changning.

00:35:37.600 --> 00:35:38.910 line:80%
I arranged for 2 subordinates

00:35:38.910 --> 00:35:40.240 line:80%
to keep looking for her.

00:35:42.200 --> 00:35:43.660 line:80%
Thank you so much, My Lord.

00:35:44.800 --> 00:35:46.130 line:80%
Let's go. Stop looking.

00:35:56.470 --> 00:35:57.990 line:80%
My... my falcon!

00:36:00.160 --> 00:36:01.680 line:80%
Yan... Yan Zheng?

00:36:12.390 --> 00:36:13.990 line:80%
Long time no see, silly bird.

00:36:14.160 --> 00:36:15.210 line:80%
Still so fat.

00:36:20.870 --> 00:36:21.600 line:80%
Go now.

00:36:29.050 --> 00:36:30.810 line:80%
[Changning and I are both fine.]

00:36:30.810 --> 00:36:32.580 line:80%
[Send Changning back to Jizhou
as soon as possible.]

00:36:32.600 --> 00:36:34.450 line:80%
[You have nothing to worry about.
Yan Zheng]

00:36:34.990 --> 00:36:36.030 line:80%
Changning...

00:36:36.720 --> 00:36:37.640 line:80%
is fine.

00:36:38.200 --> 00:36:39.120 line:80%
Yan Zheng?

00:36:41.470 --> 00:36:42.870 line:80%
Does it say that

00:36:42.870 --> 00:36:44.600 line:80%
Yan Zheng has found Changning?

00:36:45.830 --> 00:36:46.890 line:80%
Changning is fine.

00:36:47.830 --> 00:36:49.160 line:80%
Yan Zheng is fine too.

00:36:49.950 --> 00:36:50.990 line:80%
He tells you not to worry.

00:36:50.990 --> 00:36:53.790 line:80%
He will send her back to Jizhou
as soon as possible.

00:36:57.160 --> 00:36:58.200 line:80%
Good.

00:37:00.910 --> 00:37:02.600 line:80%
Good.

00:37:04.430 --> 00:37:05.730 line:80%
Changning is fine.

00:37:06.870 --> 00:37:08.120 line:80%
Yan Zheng is fine too.

00:37:10.470 --> 00:37:11.200 line:80%
Good.

00:37:11.870 --> 00:37:12.680 line:80%
Good.

00:37:17.430 --> 00:37:18.200 line:80%
My Lord.

00:37:19.990 --> 00:37:21.250 line:80%
It's an urgent matter.

00:37:22.200 --> 00:37:22.870 line:80%
There are seats inside.

00:37:22.870 --> 00:37:23.510 line:80%
Okay.

00:37:23.770 --> 00:37:25.740 line:80%
[He]

00:37:25.160 --> 00:37:27.220 line:80%
So that's all the news we have for now.

00:37:27.350 --> 00:37:28.720 line:80%
What do you two think?

00:37:33.390 --> 00:37:34.240 line:80%
Master.

00:37:35.080 --> 00:37:35.940 line:80%
Here, Mr. Zhao.

00:37:38.600 --> 00:37:39.250 line:80%
Careful!

00:37:42.080 --> 00:37:43.030 line:80%
It's hot.

00:37:47.990 --> 00:37:49.460 line:80%
Why didn't you drink?

00:37:52.510 --> 00:37:53.510 line:80%
Lord Li,

00:37:53.830 --> 00:37:56.280 line:80%
what did you mean by that?

00:37:56.280 --> 00:37:57.810 line:80%
I didn't quite understand.

00:37:57.870 --> 00:37:58.870 line:80%
Simply put,

00:37:59.030 --> 00:38:01.350 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an was surrounded
by 30,000 troops in the mountain.

00:38:01.350 --> 00:38:02.880 line:80%
He lacks food and medicine.

00:38:04.560 --> 00:38:06.560 line:80%
He wants to hold Mount Gu

00:38:06.950 --> 00:38:08.720 line:80%
to keep Shi Yue's army occupied.

00:38:08.720 --> 00:38:11.240 line:80%
It is a diversion.

00:38:11.560 --> 00:38:12.470 line:80%
The goal is to prevent

00:38:12.470 --> 00:38:16.200 line:80%
Shi Yue's army from joining forces
with Lord Changxin.

00:38:16.870 --> 00:38:18.760 line:80%
If Mount Gu falls

00:38:19.030 --> 00:38:20.640 line:80%
and the two armies merge,

00:38:20.640 --> 00:38:22.430 line:80%
Lucheng will surely be breached,

00:38:22.430 --> 00:38:23.990 line:80%
and we might lose Jizhou.

00:38:26.390 --> 00:38:27.830 line:80%
The most important thing now

00:38:27.830 --> 00:38:30.990 line:80%
is to send the provisions to Mount Gu.

00:38:31.280 --> 00:38:32.160 line:80%
I'll do it.

00:38:32.510 --> 00:38:34.030 line:80%
I don't care who he is,

00:38:34.030 --> 00:38:35.470 line:80%
I will send the grain to the mountain.

00:38:35.470 --> 00:38:36.680 line:80%
Mrs. Fan, you absolutely must not.

00:38:36.680 --> 00:38:37.990 line:80%
It is far too dangerous.

00:38:37.990 --> 00:38:38.910 line:80%
Exactly.

00:38:38.910 --> 00:38:41.390 line:80%
This isn't something
for common folk like us to do.

00:38:41.390 --> 00:38:43.760 line:80%
We should just help out here
at the Wu River Camp

00:38:43.760 --> 00:38:45.390 line:80%
and do our best.

00:38:45.390 --> 00:38:46.430 line:80%
What are you going there for?

00:38:46.430 --> 00:38:47.760 line:80%
To throw your life away?

00:38:48.120 --> 00:38:49.200 line:80%
If I don't go—

00:38:49.200 --> 00:38:50.560 line:80%
Lord Li has to deliver grain to Lucheng

00:38:50.560 --> 00:38:51.470 line:80%
so he can't go either—

00:38:51.470 --> 00:38:52.430 line:80%
then who will?

00:38:53.390 --> 00:38:55.680 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an
is fighting for us commoners.

00:38:55.680 --> 00:38:57.510 line:80%
I can't let him go hungry.

00:38:59.470 --> 00:39:00.510 line:80%
Mr. Zhao,

00:39:00.760 --> 00:39:02.470 line:80%
just let me go.

00:39:02.470 --> 00:39:04.430 line:80%
What if something happens to you?

00:39:04.430 --> 00:39:05.830 line:80%
How would I explain it to your Mrs. Zhao,

00:39:05.830 --> 00:39:06.950 line:80%
to Changning,

00:39:06.950 --> 00:39:09.510 line:80%
or to your late parents?

00:39:09.830 --> 00:39:10.720 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:39:10.910 --> 00:39:12.310 line:80%
I have my own squad now.

00:39:12.310 --> 00:39:13.710 line:80%
I can take care of myself.

00:39:13.830 --> 00:39:15.760 line:80%
How can you take care of yourself?

00:39:17.390 --> 00:39:18.680 line:80%
She has guts.

00:39:18.680 --> 00:39:21.310 line:80%
Truly the girl I chose.

00:39:22.390 --> 00:39:24.640 line:80%
Why are you here fanning the flames?

00:39:25.760 --> 00:39:28.390 line:80%
She's no longer a butcher girl.

00:39:28.430 --> 00:39:30.640 line:80%
She can lead troops in battle.

00:39:42.270 --> 00:39:44.200 line:80%
March swiftly without slackening!

00:39:44.200 --> 00:39:45.600 line:80%
Follow military orders strictly!

00:39:45.600 --> 00:39:46.640 line:80%
Yes!

00:39:47.200 --> 00:39:48.350 line:80%
Set off!

00:40:01.370 --> 00:40:03.220 line:80%
[Sui]

00:40:04.430 --> 00:40:05.290 line:80%
Your Lordship,

00:40:05.470 --> 00:40:07.720 line:80%
the torches down the mountain
stretch out like a dragon.

00:40:07.720 --> 00:40:08.910 line:80%
At a rough estimate,

00:40:09.160 --> 00:40:11.090 line:80%
there are no fewer than 30,000 men.

00:40:25.990 --> 00:40:26.680 line:80%
Jiuheng?

00:40:28.120 --> 00:40:29.640 line:80%
Give me a straight answer.

00:40:29.640 --> 00:40:31.240 line:80%
What exactly is on your mind?

00:40:31.350 --> 00:40:33.080 line:80%
Keep them under surveillance.

00:40:33.760 --> 00:40:34.600 line:80%
Yes.

00:40:36.640 --> 00:40:37.830 line:80%
That brat, the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:40:37.830 --> 00:40:39.430 line:80%
certainly found a good spot.

00:40:39.510 --> 00:40:42.040 line:80%
There is only one hidden path
up the mountain.

00:40:42.240 --> 00:40:43.430 line:80%
If our army attacks,

00:40:43.430 --> 00:40:45.030 line:80%
they can strike first.

00:40:46.030 --> 00:40:47.430 line:80%
It's really easy to defend
and hard to attack.

00:40:47.430 --> 00:40:48.760 line:80%
It will be a tough fight.

00:40:49.560 --> 00:40:50.910 line:80%
That he raided Beijue

00:40:50.910 --> 00:40:52.440 line:80%
and bathed Jinzhou in blood

00:40:52.830 --> 00:40:55.310 line:80%
wasn't just luck.

00:40:55.470 --> 00:40:56.200 line:80%
Brother,

00:40:56.470 --> 00:40:58.640 line:80%
if we can't find a way
up the mountain tonight,

00:40:58.640 --> 00:41:00.560 line:80%
we'll have to launch
a frontal assault tomorrow.

00:41:00.560 --> 00:41:01.470 line:80%
We can't.

00:41:02.310 --> 00:41:04.640 line:80%
The Heir Apparent is still in their hands.

00:41:04.720 --> 00:41:06.310 line:80%
We must not act rashly.

00:41:08.600 --> 00:41:10.330 line:80%
With Sui Yuanqing in our hands,

00:41:10.350 --> 00:41:12.150 line:80%
we can stall for as long as we can.

00:41:12.280 --> 00:41:13.870 line:80%
It depends on whether He Jingyuan

00:41:13.870 --> 00:41:15.400 line:80%
will disappoint me.

00:41:17.680 --> 00:41:18.390 line:80%
Xie Wu,

00:41:18.560 --> 00:41:20.820 line:80%
how long will the food we brought up last?

00:41:20.950 --> 00:41:23.030 line:80%
Ten days if we eat our fill.

00:41:23.030 --> 00:41:24.240 line:80%
If we make porridge with wild vegetables,

00:41:24.240 --> 00:41:25.570 line:80%
it can last half a month.

00:41:29.390 --> 00:41:31.350 line:80%
The mountain roads here are complex.

00:41:31.350 --> 00:41:33.510 line:80%
Shi Yue surrounds us without attacking,

00:41:33.510 --> 00:41:36.190 line:80%
aiming to trap us to our deaths
on the mountain.

00:41:36.910 --> 00:41:39.710 line:80%
This tactic is called
"catching a turtle in a jar."

00:41:40.200 --> 00:41:42.060 line:80%
Who is the jar and who is the turtle

00:41:42.080 --> 00:41:43.140 line:80%
remains to be seen.

00:41:43.680 --> 00:41:44.310 line:80%
Report!

00:41:45.160 --> 00:41:45.870 line:80%
Your Lordship,

00:41:45.870 --> 00:41:47.240 line:80%
a grain transport team from Jizhou

00:41:47.240 --> 00:41:48.910 line:80%
risked their lives to climb the mountain.

00:41:48.910 --> 00:41:51.100 line:80%
They broke through Shi Hu's encirclement?

00:41:51.100 --> 00:41:51.770 line:80%
Yes.

00:41:52.120 --> 00:41:53.380 line:80%
Casualties are heavy.

00:41:55.080 --> 00:41:56.640 line:80%
Make sure they are well settled.

00:41:56.640 --> 00:41:57.240 line:80%
Yes.

00:41:58.810 --> 00:41:59.600 line:80%
General!

00:41:59.760 --> 00:42:00.830 line:80%
A small grain transport team

00:42:00.830 --> 00:42:01.830 line:80%
came up the mountain
through the small path.

00:42:01.830 --> 00:42:03.570 line:80%
Our vanguard detected them.

00:42:03.680 --> 00:42:05.660 line:80%
We intended to ambush them from behind,

00:42:05.660 --> 00:42:07.490 line:80%
but the Xie Army suddenly intervened.

00:42:07.490 --> 00:42:08.510 line:80%
During the fierce battle,

00:42:08.510 --> 00:42:10.280 line:80%
we killed over ten of their men,

00:42:10.280 --> 00:42:11.680 line:80%
but a few survivors

00:42:11.680 --> 00:42:13.280 line:80%
were rescued by the Xie Army.

00:42:13.950 --> 00:42:15.680 line:80%
How did you guard the mountain?

00:42:16.120 --> 00:42:18.240 line:80%
You let them send grain up
at this critical moment!

00:42:18.240 --> 00:42:19.640 line:80%
A bunch of useless fools!

00:42:21.510 --> 00:42:22.990 line:80%
It's just a few people.

00:42:24.150 --> 00:42:26.620 line:80%
The grain they brought
wouldn't fill an ant.

00:42:26.990 --> 00:42:28.390 line:80%
There's nothing to fear.

00:42:29.870 --> 00:42:31.000 line:80%
What did they bring?

00:42:31.830 --> 00:42:33.990 line:80%
We only found grain on the bodies.

00:42:34.280 --> 00:42:36.200 line:80%
Later, in the carriage they abandoned
at the foot of the hill,

00:42:36.200 --> 00:42:37.530 line:80%
we found salt and herbs.

00:42:38.800 --> 00:42:41.310 line:80%
They must be so short on manpower

00:42:41.950 --> 00:42:44.610 line:80%
that they abandoned everything else
for grain.

00:42:49.470 --> 00:42:51.200 line:80%
Short of salt, huh?

00:42:53.030 --> 00:42:54.910 line:80%
That is good news.

00:43:03.030 --> 00:43:03.890 line:80%
Your Lordship,

00:43:05.120 --> 00:43:07.950 line:80%
there are two female medics
on the grain transport crew.

00:43:07.950 --> 00:43:09.150 line:80%
They asked to see you.

00:43:12.870 --> 00:43:13.830 line:80%
Female medics?

00:43:17.280 --> 00:43:17.990 line:80%
Bring them in.